column5: I JUST QUIT MY JOB!!!!   :lol:   RFS
More time to fish! Can you still afford bait?
I hope for the good reason(s).
Great news!!!  My father has been looking for a job for the past 3 months, hopefully there will be some openings!
What was your job??

I sold Parts @ Benson' for the past 3 yrs or so......  But before quitting .. I made sure I had another job .  I am returning to work for Community Living....where everyday you make a difference in someone's life.  RFS
Good for you Randy!
It's nice to get paid to help out others.  Congrets on the new job!
funny I thought about quiting my job  today also.....
Thank You!!  That's what I used to do before taking the Partsman job.  Working with the Developmentally Challenged is very very rewarding, challenging and FUN!!  RFS
can you still afford food? you need food
No problems here...  I have a job lined up and already have a few offers to consider... I only quit 5 hours ago.  I fish therefore I have food..  RFS
I just quit my job at UFD United Floral Distributors at 4:30 today. I am going back driving a tow truck.  :D  :D  :D  :D  :D  Jeff
yep do what ya love ,otherwise work really does suck
good you need lots of food.
Enough with the food in every post!  EDIT: Sorry mods
Find a job you love and you'll never "work" another day in your life!  Good for you Randy..
I agree Dan.
When I woke up this morning I really thought the mods would have addressed this by now.
It has been addressed.
